            "title": "滬指開市跌10點 深成指跌53點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以4103點開市，跌10點或0.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報14102點，亦跌53點或0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌4點或0.09%，開報4714點；創業板指數開市報3270點，跌7點或0.24%。</p>\n</div>",
