        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段跟跌 恒指跌90點報26397點 創維復牌高開42.66%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華爾街股市昨晚急挫，進一步影響全球股市氣氛，港股今早開市初段亦向下。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數開市報26397點，跌90點或0.34%。恒生科技指數開報5643點，跌39點或0.7%；國企指數以9067點開市，跌27點或0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創維集團(00751)擬回購及退市，同時分派創維光伏及將之在港上市；該股今早復牌大幅高開42.66%，報7.39元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：創維集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260121_FI_source-web_00751-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：創維集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260121_FI_source-web_00751-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：創維集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">TCL電子(01070)與Sony訂立合作意向備忘，該股今早再漲14.97%，報12.52元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">ASMPT(00522)評估SMT解決方案分部策略方案，包括將之出售或分拆；該股今早開報98.45元，升0.87%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"TCL電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01070-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"TCL電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/01070-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">TCL電子官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昭衍新藥(06127)料去年純利升最多3.71倍，該股今早開報26元，升4.42%。中國龍工(03339)發盈喜，該股今早亦高開1.91%，報3.2元。莎莎國際(00178)上季營業額與港澳同店銷售均升逾10%，該股今早開報0.6元，升1.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15598784-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%b7%9f%e8%b7%8c-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c90%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126397%e9%bb%9e-%e5%89%b5%e7%b6%ad%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b42",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-21 09:29:08",
